drinking so the damn neighbours can see.

126
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,193
They're all asleep.

127
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,633
Where were you?

128
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:45,357
Playing cards. I told you.

129
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:48,074
I forgot.

130
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:50,432
You always forget.

131
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:58,390
I don't want you out here
drinking anymore.

132
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,834
Rachel?

133
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:44,278
That's your name, isn't it? Rachel Munro.

134
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:46,876
- Do I know you?
- We met last night.

135
00:14:46,960 --> 00:14:48,313
Last night?

136
00:14:50,840 --> 00:14:54,230
